印度是一個[[農業國家|農業國家]]，約60%的人口直接或間接地依賴於[[農業|農業]]謀生。'''[[農民|農民]][[自殺|自殺]]佔[[印度|印度]]所有自殺的11.2%'''，學者認為他們自殺是因為農作物因天氣而失收、債務負擔高昂、政府政策影響生計、個人[[心理健康|心理健康]]和家庭問題等因素<ref>Gruère, G. & Sengupta, D. (2011), Bt cotton and farmer suicides in India: an evidence-based assessment, The Journal of Development Studies, 47(2), 316-337</ref><ref>Schurman, R. (2013), Shadow space: suicides and the predicament of rural India, Journal of Peasant Studies, 40(3), 597-601</ref><ref>Das, A. (2011), Farmers’ suicide in India: implications for public mental health, International Journal of Social Psychiatry, 57(1), 21-29</ref>。2012年，{{link-en|印度國家犯罪記錄局|National Crime Records Bureau}}的統計數字指該年印度有13,754名農民自殺<ref name=ncrb2012>National Crime Reports Bureau, [http://ncrb.nic.in/CD-ADSI-2012/ADSI2012.pdf ADSI Report Annual - 2012] {{Wayback|url=http://ncrb.nic.in/CD-ADSI-2012/ADSI2012.pdf |date=20130810222918 }} Government of India, Page 242, Table 2.11</ref>。

== 概論 ==
印度農民自殺問題始於20世紀90年代，其中[[馬哈拉施特拉邦|馬哈拉施特拉邦]]首先出現農民自殺的個案，不久[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]也發生了類似事件<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://specials.rediff.com/news/2007/nov/22sld1.htm |title=Rediff News |access-date=2014-07-29 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211051505/http://specials.rediff.com/news/2007/nov/22sld1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然印度政府未曾作出印度農民分佈的研究，但有說法指大多數農民自殺事件是發生在[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]、[[馬哈拉施特拉邦|馬哈拉施特拉邦]]、[[卡納塔克邦|卡納塔克邦]]、[[喀拉拉邦|喀拉拉邦]]和[[旁遮普邦|旁遮普邦]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Debts and Drought Drive India's Farmers to Despair |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2004/06/06/world/debts-and-drought-drive-india-s-farmers-to-despair.html |date=June 6, 2004 |publisher=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |page= |first=Amy |last=Waldman |accessdate=2010-05-02 |archive-date=2021-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214200021/https://www.nytimes.com/2004/06/06/world/debts-and-drought-drive-india-s-farmers-to-despair.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=India acts over suicide crisis on farms |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/india-acts-over-suicide-crisis-on-farms-551762.html |date=2 July 2004 |publisher=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |page= |location=London |first=Justin |last=Huggler |accessdate=2010-05-02 |archive-date=2011-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110922060852/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/india-acts-over-suicide-crisis-on-farms-551762.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。印度農民自殺問題頗為嚴峻，迫使了一些地方政府成立專責辦公室，處理農民自殺問題<ref name="VNSS Mission">{{Cite web |url=http://www.vnss-mission.gov.in/ |title=VNSS Mission |access-date=2014-07-29 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126111045/http://www.vnss-mission.gov.in/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 原因 ==
[[File:Farmer_suicide.png|thumb]]
印度農民自殺背後的原因眾說紛紜<ref>{{cite web|title=Risks, Farmers’ Suicides and Agrarian Crisis in India: Is There A Way Out?|author=Mishra, Srijit|publisher=Indira Gandhi Institute of Development Research (IGIDR)|year=2007|url=http://www.igidr.ac.in/pdf/publication/WP-2007-014.pdf|accessdate=2014-07-29|archive-date=2017-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517085143/http://www.igidr.ac.in/pdf/publication/WP-2007-014.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Behere PB, Behere AP. Farmers' suicide in Vidarbha region of Maharashtra state: A myth or reality?. Indian J Psychiatry [serial online] 2008 [cited 2009 Oct 23];50:124-7. Available from: http://www.indianjpsychiatry.org/text.asp?2008/50/2/124/42401 {{Wayback|url=http://www.indianjpsychiatry.org/text.asp?2008%2F50%2F2%2F124%2F42401 |date=20181005183632 }}</ref><ref>Stone, Glenn Davis, 2007. "Agricultural Deskilling and the Spread of Genetically Modified Cotton in Warangal." ''Current Anthropology'' 48:67-103</ref>。2004年至2006年間有研究指出有數個原因，如信用制度有風險、[[旱灾|旱灾]]影響農業生產、農業收入差、缺乏替代性的收入機會、經濟低迷、缺乏適當的心理輔導等<ref name = "Gruere">{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpri.org/sites/default/files/publications/ifpridp00808.pdf|year=2008|title=Bt Cotton and Farmer Suicides in India: Reviewing the Evidence|author=Guillaume P. Gruère, Purvi Mehta-Bhatt and Debdatta Sengupta|publisher=International Food Policy Research Institute|access-date=2014-07-29|archive-date=2015-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150616201527/http://www.ifpri.org/sites/default/files/publications/ifpridp00808.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Nagraj">{{cite web |author=Nagraj, K. |year=2008 |title=Farmers suicide in India: magnitudes, trends and spatial patterns |url=http://www.macroscan.com/anl/mar08/pdf/Farmers_Suicides.pdf |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110512173317/http://www.macroscan.com/anl/mar08/pdf/Farmers_Suicides.pdf |archivedate=2011-05-12 |accessdate=2014-07-29 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Risks, Farmers' Suicides and Agrarian Crisis in India: Is There A Way Out?|author=Mishra, Srijit|publisher=Indira Gandhi Institute of Development Research (IGIDR)|year=2007|url=http://www.igidr.ac.in/pdf/publication/WP-2007-014.pdf|accessdate=2014-07-29|archive-date=2017-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517085143/http://www.igidr.ac.in/pdf/publication/WP-2007-014.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2004年，[[孟買高等法院|孟買高等法院]]要求{{link-en|塔塔社會科學院|Tata Institute of Social Sciences}}提交報告，調查農民自殺問題<ref name=InfoChange>Staff, InfoChange August 2005. [http://infochangeindia.org/agriculture/books-a-reports/644-farmer-suicides-in-maharashtra-since-2001-says-tiss-report.html 644 farmer suicides in Maharashtra since 2001, says TISS report] {{Wayback|url=http://infochangeindia.org/agriculture/books-a-reports/644-farmer-suicides-in-maharashtra-since-2001-says-tiss-report.html |date=20160307171856 }}</ref><ref name=TataReport>Dandekar A, et al, Tata Institute. [http://www.vnss-mission.gov.in/htmldocs/Farmers_suicide_TISS_report.pdf Causes of Farmer Suicides in Maharashtra: An Enquiry. Final Report Submitted to the Mumbai High Court March 15, 2005] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vnss-mission.gov.in/htmldocs/Farmers_suicide_TISS_report.pdf |date=20130809074417 }}</ref>，調查報告指政府冷漠，農民缺乏安全感，又不能獲取與農業有關的資訊，令他們感到絕望<ref name=InfoChange />。2012年也有關於印度農民自殺的研究，指農民自殺的主要原因是債務、酒精成癮、環境、[[通貨膨脹|通貨膨脹]]、壓力、家庭責任、農業成本增加等<ref name=dnd>Dongre and Deshmukh, Farmers’ suicides in the Vidarbha region of Maharashtra, India: a qualitative exploration of their causes, Journal of Injury and Violence Research, Jan 2012; 4(1): 2–6</ref>；2006年則有研究指債務和經濟狀況是農民自殺的主要因素<ref name=bnb>Behere and Bhise, Farmers' suicide: Across culture, Indian Journal of Psychiatry, 2009 Oct-Dec; 51(4): 242–243</ref>。

